\id 3JN - Urat NT (PNGBTA); Hilkka Arminen (SIL Advisor); 25-Nov-2015
\h 3 JON
\toc3 3Jo
\toc2 3 Jon
\toc1 Tup hun ŋaiye Jon nainge
\mt2 Tup hun ŋaiye
\mt1 Jon nainge
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Apo 19.29, Rom 16.23, 1Ko 1.14\x*Ŋam Jon, miyeꞌ embep ende ŋoto sios, mainge tup eꞌe malme nin toꞌ ŋam Gaius. Ŋoihmbwaip ŋam hriphrip me nin ŋembere sekete.
\v 2 Topoꞌe ŋam sisyeme nange ŋoihmbwaip nin ki sai bwore. Taꞌe luku pe, ŋemei ŋam, ŋam si misilihme Got ŋaiye ka embepteme nin no, na orp bwore pe, ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe lalme ŋaiye na ende ka el bwore.
\v 3 Ŋam hriphrip supule, ŋupe ŋaiye lenge toꞌ tatai syeꞌ yate jere leꞌe pe, tinge yana ŋam nange nin narp bwore miꞌ supule, topoꞌe nin ŋende ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe gande wusyep mise.
\v 4 Ŋam hriphrip supule ŋaiye ŋam masande nange lenge talah ŋam tinge jande wusyep mise.
\s1 Gaius ŋende wah bwore
\p 
\v 5 Ŋemei ŋam, yaŋah uku ŋaiye nin ŋende pe, ki bwore supule ŋupe ŋaiye nin nungwisme lenge toꞌ tatai syeꞌ ŋaiye yukur ŋemei nin.
\v 6 Syeꞌ tinge si yate jere leꞌe yana poi sios ŋaiye nin ŋende ŋoihmbwaip bwore nal me tinge. Ŋemei ŋam, ungwis lenge ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe ŋaiye tinge seheiꞌe ŋupe ŋaiye ka yil yaŋah no, ka yende wah tikin Got pe, luku ka ende Got ka hriphrip.
\v 7 Tinge yalꞌe yalꞌe yende wah tikin Krais pe, tinge yukur yisilihme lenge haiten miyeꞌ tuweinge ŋaiye ka yambaꞌe ŋainde me tinge, pakai.
\v 8 Taꞌe luku pe, poi ya mungwis lenge miyeꞌ taꞌe luku no, ya lalme gwin tuꞌe ŋaiye miyeꞌ wah no, ya mende bongolme wusyep bwore mise.
\s1 Diotrepes ŋende pupwa
\p 
\v 9 Ŋam si mainge wusyep syeꞌ member malme lenge Kristen miyeꞌ tuweinge lalme ŋaiye yarp moi nin. Kom Diotrepes, kin ŋasande ŋaiye ka orp miyeꞌ ondoh tinge, kut kin yukur ŋasande wusyep poi.
\v 10 Taꞌe luku pe, ŋupe ŋaiye ma mut pe, ma mini yip ŋaimune ŋaiye kin ŋende, topoꞌe wusyep pupwa syeꞌ ŋaiye kin gonombaiꞌe poi. Topoꞌe yukur kin ŋende ŋai ilyeh uku, kin plihe garnge ŋaiye ka ende nihararme lenge Kristen jetmam syeꞌ, topoꞌe ŋanange pakai me lenge lahmende ŋaiye da yungwisme tinge. Ŋaiye ka yende pe, ka ginyen lenge el tus wicherꞌ me sios.
\s1 Demitrius ŋende ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe bwore
\p 
\v 11 Ŋemei ŋam, yukur na ende ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe pupwa gunde kin ŋaiye ŋende, na pakai. Kut ende ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe gunde ŋaiye ki bwore. Lahmende ŋaiye ŋende ŋaiꞌe ŋaiꞌe bwore pe, kin uku talah tikin Got. O lahmende ŋaiye ŋende pupwa pe, kin yukur sisyeme Got.
\v 12 Lenge Kristen toꞌ tatai sisyeme Demitrius pe, tinge yahraꞌe naŋ kin ŋaiye kin miyeꞌ bwore. Kin gande wusyep mise supule tikin Got bworerme. Pe poi topoꞌe mahraꞌe naŋ kin pe, yip sisyeme nange wusyep poi ki bwore mise.
\p 
\v 13 Wusyep ŋam wula wula ŋaiye ma mini yip, kom ŋam gwarnge ŋaiye ma minge guh tup member yip mil, pakai.
\v 14 Ŋam ŋoihmeryembe ŋaiye sehei ma muta metekeꞌ yip, topoꞌe yip pa yetekeꞌ ŋam pe, ya mininge wusyep.
\v 15 Hriphrip topoꞌe ŋoihmbwaip ŋumwaiye sai topoꞌe yip. Lenge ŋimei ŋam, syeꞌ tinge yember wusyep hriphrip yalme yip. Hriphrip ŋam nal me yip ilyeh ilyeh tongonose, lenge ŋimei ŋam. 
